.SH NAME
bareai-doctor - Run ranked diagnostics with read-only suggestions


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbareai doctor [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Analyze host, GPU, Docker, and LLM state and report ranked findings with what/why/try hints.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for doctor

.PP
\fB--severity\fP="info"
	minimum severity to show (info|warn|critical)


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB-j\fP, \fB--json\fP[=false]
	output in JSON format

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	disable colored output

.PP
\fB--timeout\fP=10s
	timeout for probes and API calls


.SH EXAMPLE
.EX
  bareai doctor
  bareai doctor --severity warn
  bareai doctor --json | jq '.findings[] | select(.severity=="warn")'
.EE


